jops.server
Class SpiPlayer

java.lang.Object
  jops.server.SpiPlayer
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable, FilePlayer, Player
public class SpiPlayer
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, FilePlayer

A player node to play any music file supported by the Java Sound System - that is, any music file with an SPI available. The system, by default, packs a FLAC SPI (jflac).

Author:
Matt Windsor
